NOTE ON RAW DATA:

The raw series stored under 01_data_raw/ originate from the Banco Central de
la República Dominicana (BCRD) and are public information under Dominican Law
6-04 on access to public information. This CC BY 4.0 license covers ONLY the
work of curating, splicing, consolidating and reorganizing those series into
the present dataset. The underlying observations remain BCRD's public data.

The third-party documents referenced by the analysis (BCRD's Informe de
Política Monetaria diciembre 2025, and Jiménez P. & López H. 2014) are NOT
redistributed in this repository. See the README for the original sources.
